    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Up for sale is a functional vehicle in fair condition. While it remains a reliable option for getting from point A to point B, please note that it shows visible signs of age including some cosmetic wear on the interior and exterior, as well as minor mechanical quirks that are common for its mileage. The engine starts up fine and it remains drivable, but it could benefit from some TLC and eventual maintenance to bring it back to peak form. This is an honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of character.",
