    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and fading on the clear coat in a few spots. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and typical wear on the driver's seat bolster. It runs and drives well, though it may require some minor mechanical attention or routine maintenance soon to keep it in top shape. This is an honest, functional car for someone looking for affordable transportation without the new-car price tag.",
